headline: Here’s Why The Bank of New York Mellon Corporation (BK) Rose in Q3
summary: Parnassus Investments, an investment management company, released the “Parnassus Value Equity Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the Fund (Investor Shares) returned 7.28% (net of fees) underperforming the Russell 1000 Value Index’s 9.43% return. headline: 3 Financial Stocks to Secure Your Investments Before Year-End
summary: Finance stocks are expected to reap the benefits of technology advancements, growing premiums and favorable consumer spending as they head into 2025. However, inflationary challenges might act as a partial offset.
